dct_description_sm: This polygon data layer represents tax parcels for Door County, Wisconsin in 2015. The dataset was originally published by the Door County Real Property Listing Office in 2015.[The Tax Parcel map of Door County, Wisconsin. This was derived from a variety of source maps including survey plats, deed descriptions, subdivision maps, certified survey maps, easements, and right-of-way plats. These source materials were of several different scales and were from dates ranging from the late 1800's to the present. This map provides a useful representation of the geometry and topology of tax parcels and is suitable for its intended purpose. It is not, however, meant to be used for the determination of land ownership and interest descriptions contained in individual deeds.]
